{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "約束されざる地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-5", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "アイコンタクト", "storyInfo": "ライン生命とゴードンの秘密が揃って暴かれ、エキスポの準備は停滞した。しかし特殊事故の審判を行うための公聴会が一向に行われない。スカイが人を引き連れてライン生命の「木」を守ろうとする。ギュスターヴとマイレンダーも強引にパークに介入した。しかしこの時、キーパーソンであるナスティが行方をくらました。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g13_trimountlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$act15_intro", "key": "$act15_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "f", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*クルビアスラング*空に浮いてるあの木は一体どういうことだ？", "name": "怒る企業代表"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エキスポまであと数日しかないのに、木が何社分の展示ブースを占領したか数えてみたか？　そもそもライン生命は上層での展示権限を申請してないんだぞ！", "name": "怒る企業代表"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絶対にライン生命と管理局の役人が裏でつながってるんだ！　昨日この目で一部始終を見たんだぞ。パーク総責任者のゴードンがあの木の上にいたんだ！", "name": "焦る企業代表"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それで元管理局局長のギュスターヴがラジオで、明朝に説明を行うと約束した。それがどうだ？", "name": "焦る企業代表"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もうこの時間だぞ、なのに公聴会の情報が全く入ってこない。時間稼ぎをしてるんだろう！", "name": "焦る企業代表"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "皆様、どうか落ち着いてください。", "name": "スタッフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今回の件は、数百の企業からのサイエンスパークのエンジニア部門と総務部門への信用問題にかかわるため、時間を要して慎重に対処しております。できる限り皆様が納得いく対処案を出す予定です。", "name": "スタッフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰が慎重に対処しろって言った？", "name": "怒る企業代表"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい？", "name": "スタッフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空に昇ったのは二つ目のリングラボじゃないんだ。いちいち大騒ぎする必要はないだろう？", "name": "怒る企業代表"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エンジニア部門の点検はとっくに終わっているし、総務部門の資格審査も終わっている。こんな時期にパークの部門責任者の汚職なんざ誰が気にするんだ？", "name": "怒る企業代表"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ですが、公聴会の開催は必要な監察手順でして……", "name": "スタッフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調査だろうが審判だろうがそっちの勝手だ。こっちはただ公聴会の最終結果が知りたいだけなんだ――", "name": "焦る企業代表"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結局、クルビアどころかテラ全体を揺るがすこと間違いなしの「天空の暮らし博覧会」は、開催されるのか？", "name": "焦る企業代表"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g9_treeplatform_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どけ。", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-80", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sit_tatami", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もう一度言うぞ。どけ。", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "スカイ"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここに座っていれば、お前たちの背後にある違法設備に手を出せないとでも思ってるのか？", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここの設備は公聴会が始まるまではライン生命の財産だ。それに、違法設備だと？", "name": "スカイ"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警備員さん、これがただの「浮遊プランターユニット」だってわからないのか？　その隣に浮いている苗と、俺たちの背後にあるこいつは、何一つ変わらないぞ？", "name": "スカイ"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屁理屈を……おい、誰か来い！", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "30,0", "duration": 1.2}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "-30,0", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……スカイ、こっちの人数はそんなに多くないわ。もし警備員たちが強硬手段を取ってきたら、長くはもたない。", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それに私たちの後ろにある樹形装置に危険性があるかどうかはわからないのよ。だって二年前、クリステン統括も……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺から言いたいことは一つだけだ。あんたは科学者としてナスティ主任の研究成果をみすみす他人に差し出すことなんて受け入れられるのか？", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいえ、でも……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_529_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なら行動しろ。後悔しないようにな。", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちっ、ライン生命のパーク滞在人数には制限がかかっている、やはり人手が足りない、もし……", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おいおいスカイさんよ、俺たちもライン生命に雇われてるってことを忘れてないか？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.7}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんたたちを巻き込むつもりはない。", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公聴会の調査のことか？　いらん心配はよせ。無実の罪なんか俺たちは見慣れてるだろ。", "name": "モニターB"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さっさと呼んでくれたら、警備員どもは浮遊プラットフォームに上がってくることすらできなかったかもしれないのに。", "name": "モニターA"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何だ、スラムから集められたモニターがヒーロー気どりか？", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "違法な設備を秘匿し、他人の財物を破壊、さらに事情を知っていながら報告を怠った……これらの罪状だけでも貴様らを全員監獄送りにできるんだぞ！", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ナスティ主任が雇ってくれなかったら、今頃すでに監獄の中だったよ。", "name": "モニターB"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの木に何かするつもりなら、私たちを乗り越えてからにしなさい。", "name": "モニターA"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2045_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいだろう……暴力を受けても恨むなよ！", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ライン生命の研究員とモニターたちの壁が一歩も譲らず横暴な警備員を阻み、物好きな見物人たちがその外を囲んで、異様に目立つ「木」を見上げている。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人々の後ろから、見知らぬ大きな影が力強い足音を立て、大股で通り過ぎる。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これがライン生命の……「木」ですか。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#5$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "channel": "crowd", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お疲れ様です、先輩。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "社交辞令は結構ですよ、マーシア。私はずっと休んでいましたからね。疲れるようなことは何もありません。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公聴会へ参加されるためにいらしたのですか？", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ええ。マイレンダー応急対策管理監督協会のバッジのデザインはなかなか悪くありません。あなたもつけてみてはいかがですか。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私の任務は正式に終了したということでしょうか？", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我々の任務は始まったばかりですよ。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仰せの通りに。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話はまだ終わっていませんよ。ここ数日はアクシデントが次々と起こっていますよね。ナスティとゴードン・タネン以外、まだ私が知らない物語はありますか？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……いいえ。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よろしい。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五分後にロープウェイステーションで会いましょう。このパークは本当に広くて目が回りますから。私には「プロペラパラダイス」をじっくりと案内してくれる「現地ガイド」が必要なのですよ。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（途切れ途切れのうわ言）", "name": "ヴァエラ"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "申し訳ありません、事前に窓を閉めておくべきでした。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街では企業代表やモニターがデモを行っております。公聴会が先延ばしになればなるほど、不安になるのでしょう。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openwindow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "crowd", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お加減はいかがですか、ヴァエラさん？", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（微弱な呼吸）", "name": "ヴァエラ"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お体の状況は極めて深刻です。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "すでにナスティ主任にお会いしたのですから、河谷へお帰りの手配を――", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいえ……ここに……", "name": "ヴァエラ"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "また昨晩のように拒否されるのですね。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヴァエラさん、これから数日間、パークはより騒がしくなるでしょう。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうなってからここを離れようとしても、今のように容易くはいきませんよ。", "name": "マーシア"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomB", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "また捕まっちまった！　監房の番号まで変わってない！", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公聴会の時間も何度も変更になるし……なあ、あいつら時間を稼いでもっと多くの証拠を見つけて、いくつもの罪で一斉に罰そうとしてないか？", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先に言っとくけどさ、もし身分を訊かれたら、絶対正直に吐いてやるからな、お前の方が偽物だって！", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "おい、黙ってないでなんか言えよ、怖いんだけど……", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒野の移動監獄も、いい観光地にすることができるかもしれない。でも外から侵入するのと中から逃げ出す難易度は全然違うから、気を付けないと。", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな時まで、観光ルートの評価かよ？", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客を一人見失っただけじゃ飽き足らず、もう一人は監獄にぶち込もうってか？", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あのお客さんのことはあたしが見つけるから。あなたの方は、そんなに心配しなくていいよ。", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なんでわかるんだよ？", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尋問なし、身分確認なし、出廷命令なし……これ全部、あの警備員たちが、あたしたちの罪状をでっちあげるために時間稼ぎしているだけだって思うの？", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だってそうだろ。", "name": "オークリー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あたしはむしろ逆だと思う――", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きっとこの公聴会の主役は、あたしたちじゃないんだよ。", "name": "フェルネ"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g7_airrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "フェルネとオークリーは牢屋にぶち込まれて、マーちゃんは昨日から行方不明。登録センターの電話はいつまでも通話中で全くつながらず、誰もが俺とナスティを探している……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "よし、ついに管理局で学んだものをジジイに実演してやる時が来た。何を問われようと、俺は説明してやれる――怖い者なんざなんもねぇ！", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あはっ、老いぼれの事務効率も前より落ちたな。まだ誰も尋問に来ないとは。", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待てよ！", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふう……端末から見れる限り、俺の肩書はまだ「プロペラパラダイス」の総責任者のままだ。", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ピピ――「天空の征服者」のストレス値上昇を確認、健康上のリスクにお気を付けください。我々の目標はテラの外にあり、その道のりは遠く、任務は重大なのですから。", "name": "宇宙鱗獣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちくしょうが、公聴会は一体いつやるつもりだ？　俺が担当だったらとっくに解決していたぞ！　ジジイめ、わざと俺の邪魔をしやがったな。七年前からそうだし、今も変わらねぇ！", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "では、君はなぜ七年もの間、何一つ成長してないのかな？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ギュスターヴ長官……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言ってみたまえ。もし君であったら、どう解決するつもりだったのかな？", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ライン生命のエンジニアリングチェックが中止になった程度でうぬぼれて、これなら安心して後ろ暗い商売を続けられると思い込む……", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管理局は幼稚園ではないはずなのだが、君はなぜこれほど無邪気に育ってしまったのだろうか？", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あのクソったれな木さえなければ、全部順調だったんだ。全部ナスティのせいだ！", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順調？　ナスティの手下の助手研究員でさえ、君の手口を見抜いたのは知らないのか？", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その者が君と同じくらいに甘く、よりによって私に助けを求めたりしていなければ、君の醜態はとうに大衆に公開されていたのだよ。", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "言ってみなさい、君ならばどう解決するつもりだったのかな？", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官……どうかお助けを……", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふん。ライン生命が何を目的でこのフロート装置を隠したのかはこの際どうでもいいがね。これ以上彼らに自らの造物を定義させてはいけない。", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#8$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "君の職務怠慢のせいで、本来全権で引き受けられたはずの総務部門は評定に一切参加できなくなってしまった。", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#4$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ということは、「第三者」を導入すべきと？", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客観的で専門者で、一見中立である科学顧問を、だ。", "name": "ギュスターヴ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゴードンさん、お噂はかねがね伺っています。", "name": "科学顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2042_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外見はどうも科学顧問らしくないが……本当にライン生命のアレを対処できるのか？", "name": "ゴードン"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "評定対象をよく知るために、先ほど浮遊プラットフォームへ行ってまいりました。", "name": "科学顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2038_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うむ、実に壮大な「巨木」でしたよ。「木」の下までも賑やかでしたね。", "name": "科学顧問"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2038_1#2$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g9_treeplatform_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "やってみろよ！　できるもんなら俺たちの屍を越えてみろ！", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#6$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（スカイさん……）", "name": "モニター"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（安心しろ、わざとビビらせているだけだ。）", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ライン生命の科学者は星のさやの外の放射線に脳を焼かれたのか、血を見なけりゃ気が済まないんだな？", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "だったらその願い、叶えてやろうじゃないか！", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そこまで。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その制服……マイレンダーの人間か？", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我々はマイレンダー基金所属、応急対策管理監督協会のメンバーです。サイエンスパークの規定により、事故または災害発生時に本機構はパークに対する管理権限を委任されます。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゴードン長官とギュスターヴ氏に確認を取っても構いませんよ。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "パークの警備員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監督協会？", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、スカイさん。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お気持ちは理解できますが、どうか過激な行動はお控えください。我々にはあなたとお仲間の皆様に対して強権的な手段をとることができます。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "つまり「プロペラパラダイス」は非常事態に入っていて、昨晩の事件はそちらの初期調査では――「特殊事故」、に定義されたと？", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい。監督協会はすでに特別調査チームを立ち上げて現場と関係者からの証拠収集を始めています。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我々の調査は現在も続いています。公的な監督を行う司法機関が欠けている状態では、公聴会が唯一公正な審判手段となります。どうか辛抱強くお待ちくだされば幸いです。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公聴会が始まるまで、この「浮遊プランターユニット」に対するライン生命の所有権は認められるのか？", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もちろんです。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そちらの調査結果が、先ほど提示してくださった結論同様、公正なものであることを願っています。", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お任せください。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨時浮遊プラットフォームの安全確認、第二小隊パトロール継続。", "name": "協会メンバー"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.8}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "スカイさん、俺たち、これで引き上げるんですか？", "name": "モニター"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警備員の態度を見る限り、マイレンダーに管轄権があるのは本当なのだろう。", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "やるやると言っていた公聴会が何度も延期になっている。この後もまた何か不備が起こるかもしれないし、ここで待ち続けることは俺たちが情報を得るのに無益だ。それと……", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰か、ナスティ主任を見かけなかったか？", "name": "スカイ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}